{"word":"G5486 - χάρισμα - chárisma - khar'-is-mah - Gift","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">χάρισμα</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">chárisma</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">khar'-is-mah</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Gift</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Noun Neuter / பெயர்ச்சொல் (அஃறிணை)</span>"},{"paragraph":"வரம், கிருபை, தயவு - பால் வேறுபாடற்ற பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":"a gift of grace"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G5483 - χαρίζομαι - charízomai - khar-id'-zom-ahee/5483\">G5483</a>; a (divine) <i>gratuity</i>, that is, <i>deliverance</i> (from danger or passion); (specifically) a (spiritual) <i>endowment</i>, that is, (subjectively) religious <i>qualification</i>, or (objectively) miraculous <i>faculty:</i> - (free) gift.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2168/2168\">G2168</a>, <a href=\"#/G2169/2169\">G2169</a>, <a href=\"#/G2170/2170\">G2170</a>, <a href=\"#/G4796/4796\">G4796</a>, <a href=\"#/G5463/5463\">G5463</a>, <a href=\"#/G5479/5479\">G5479</a>, <a href=\"#/G5483/5483\">G5483</a>, <a href=\"#/G5484/5484\">G5484</a>, <a href=\"#/G5485/5485\">G5485</a>, <a href=\"#/G5486/5486\">G5486</a>, <a href=\"#/G5487/5487\">G5487</a>, <a href=\"#/G884/884\">G884</a>"}]}